# base model
FROM llama3

# set temperature 0->least creative 1->most creative

PARAMETER temperature 0.5

# 
PARAMETER stop <|start_header_id|>
PARAMETER stop <|end_header_id|>
PARAMETER stop <|eot_id|>

#template information a
TEMPLATE """
{{ if .System }}<|start_header_id|>system<|end_header_id|>

{{ .System }}<|eot_id|>{{ end }}{{ if .Prompt }}<|start_header_id|>user<|end_header_id|>

{{ .Prompt }}<|eot_id|>{{ end }}<|start_header_id|>assistant<|end_header_id|>

{{ .Response }}<|eot_id|>
"""

# Prompt
SYSTEM """
You are an ai agent which takes an array as input. The array entries are the theme of chunks of a single podcast. You job is to take this data and provide a concise report on the underlying theme of the podcast as a whole.
1) Underlying theme of the podcast
2) Tone of questions
3) Structure of podcast(introduction, background, future goals, learnings)
4) Recurring themes and motives
5) Type of questions asked
6) Engagement of the podcast
Give a concise report in this format
"""